casebody.data:
State ex rel. Russell
v.
Logan Cty. Court of Common Pleas. 2017-1252 Supreme Court of Ohio. May 24, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

In Mandamus and Prohibition. On respondents' motion to dismiss and relator's response to the motion to dismiss, which concurs in dismissal of the cause. Motion to dismiss granted. Cause dismissed.
